commit.title: Micromega: more robust  generation of cutting planes
commit.message:
Micromega: more robust  generation of cutting planes

The cutting planes are now generated from an optimal Simplex tableau.
(Previous naive cuts could loop forever or miss a cutting plane).
Anti-cycling: choose the cut with biggest index.
